message:
Task finished.

Summary:
- Implemented and tested solution at /workspace/solution.py (reads N from stdin, prints the count of integers ≤ N with exactly 9 divisors).
- Created test harness /workspace/eval_test.py and evaluation /workspace/evaluation.txt.
- Verification performed: sample N=200 → 3; large sample N=4_000_000_000_000 → 407073; exhaustive brute-force checks up to N=5000 all matched expected results.
- How to run: echo 200 | python3 /workspace/solution.py

No further action required.
